                                                 java.lang.Object... args)
        Description copied from interface: StorageInterface
        Provides a means of iteration over existing objects at a specified location. This method is particularly nice for use in for-each loops. The provided scheme is not relevant at this point, but the developer must avoid calling this method with a path of a different schema.
